{"type": "article", "id": 30553, "title": "这些漂亮的椅子，用的是废弃塑料袋织成的坐垫｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-03T23:04:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31045, "name": "Reform Studio"}, {"id": 31046, "name": "Studio Hopkins"}, {"id": 31047, "name": "Coalatree"}, {"id": 31048, "name": "FICO"}, {"id": 31049, "name": "Shao"}, {"id": 30480, "name": "Siyu Lou"}, {"id": 31050, "name": "Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte"}, {"id": 31051, "name": "何鑫"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804171440ublzM091UOryDLPX.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Diplomate by Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte</h3><p class=\"\">这个让人联想到图书馆自习桌的桌面隔断是比利时设计师 Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte 的作品，橡木框架中固定了一片折叠起来的毛毡，当中的空间可以用来存放小物。相比塑料或者金属制的隔断，浅色毛毡和橡木的组合给人的感觉更柔和温软，简洁的造型适用于各种开放式的办公环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234907y4tJW63VvEHux0js.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.641429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608032349089EF30HRD1tZQWKxf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234907fLBEDldU5CyMxNv2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234908LuE9vfsKO2aj8J3t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234907pQb5YaySgR3BtDhX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234908IHVMcXZBbQA89hNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ahwa collection by Reform Studio<br></h3><p>第一眼看到开罗 <a href=\"http://reformstudio.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Reform Studio</a> 推出的这些椅子时，你或许很难察觉它们采用的并不是普通的织物坐垫。工作室特别开发了一种名为 Plastex 的环保材料，展现出了废品利用背后无限的可能：回收的塑料袋被工匠手工拆解成线状，再通过埃及传统的手织机进行编织。由于收集到的塑料袋颜色不一，每一件成品都拥有着独一无二的多色花纹。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234854PIw0vBHJUyCuLDea.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234854zmNrJX7fevTOq1tE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234854uai7cIDSZqgKyxmG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234855tGsCfazLV0cgKEnQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234855hxRoDNOPuF8Wm6Zc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750611\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>绿加 by Siyu Lou &amp; 何鑫</h3><p>来自杭州的 Siyu Lou 和何鑫发现比起和同事面对面聊天，人们更喜欢用手机在虚拟世界进行对话。为此他们共同设计了一款名为<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/27906329/LUEJIA-Flower-Pot\" rel=\"nofollow\">绿加</a>的办公室花盆系统，希望通过这种协作种植的方式创造话题，以此增进同事间的关系。这套系统包含四种不同的花盆和一个白色的展架，花盆内置了光敏以及土壤湿度探测器，它们会为不同植物的生长情况进行评估。当花盆电量较少、植物缺水或者阳光的时候，花盆底部的 LED 灯带就会点亮相应的颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234803gFOsHPt9cIzGpVT0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234803gLuWySlCU74NsnDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234804eFopVQmBERha8lX1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608032348044sbSvew23Z8JVH7d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234804ifnPJMAc6rNh9Db0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234804VhD8SzMNmpiq0onI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Parka collection by Studio Hopkins</h3><p>到了冬天，你和你的家具或许都需要一件厚厚的外套：Studio Hopkins 推出的 Parka 系列就将羊毛织物与白蜡木结合在一起，营造出了独特的北欧风格。这种罕见的材质组合减轻了木制家具带给人们的那种坚硬感，透露着一股居家气息，简洁的造型适用于各种不同的装修风格。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.studiohopkins.com/parka-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，价格从 750 到 2950 美元不等。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234737qaF3tClPpM9NzhH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234737KCmIvMtx0Zhd3ifX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016080323473780L1iQxvDuSh6TAe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234737dgP9e6xFsBY3HO8J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234737XpkdQma0qcbv9RlM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234737lw6pHPvVsu5mzeaO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kachula V2 by Coalatree</h3><p>无论是去户外探险还是参加音乐节，毯子都是必不可少的装备，来自美国盐湖城的设计团队 <a href=\"http://www.coalatree.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coalatree</a> 发现普通的毯子并不能一次性满足人们出行时的各种需求，为此他们曾经推出过一款多功能毯子 Kachula，今天要介绍的 V2 就是它的迭代产品。最新款由防水防风的面料制成，采用了双面拉链的设计。它既可以变成一个枕头供人小憩，也可以当作兜帽穿在身上遮风挡雨。不使用的时候只要折叠成小袋塞进包里即可，携带起来非常方便。这是 Kachula 的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/coalatree/kachula-20-the-packable-multi-use-adventure-blanke\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 50 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234642Ctax0LBYAKlgzouw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234642ilRZycOU0V4M8BCL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.676471\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234642oyNpafjmGCd3KkIA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234642L4C5BWIJKtmnSUcv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234642tweSzbvIBy4YNsZr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FICO Ginger Craft Ale by Shao</h3><p>菲律宾的精酿姜汁啤酒品牌 FICO 委托 <a href=\"http://www.designbyshao.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Shao</a> 工作室设计了一组非常清新的包装。Shao 的设计师们采用了透明的瓶身，让人们可以清楚地看到啤酒的颜色，并通过简洁的白底黑字标签强调这一自产品牌所特有的“有机感”。为了区别四种不同的风味，融合了原材料颜色的圆圈代替了字母 O 出现在标签上，是一个非常有心的小细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234608nojPq2cEdyB3WZmx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234607ogWEbuVnJtF7rjUs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234609NRS5jhIveaFqQVuU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234610YSyHoV8li69XGWnL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234609ogGIET4i1w8l2Ozu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803234610572GMAzjfBdblUsa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}